{"tid":555784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個老媽子通常識，但係老豆未必識嘅技能","createTime":"2018-02-09T21:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T12:18:01.000Z","uid":43161,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d7faef734979c99c91b0e0b28e052867c25897b4","tid":555784,"uid":43161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T21:00:39.000Z","msg":"就係幫我剪頭髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由細到大都係媽子幫我剪頭髮，永遠都兩邊透薄，後面剪短，前面同頭頂剪碎嘅標準學生頭，到自己大個咗鐘意跟住班朋友去髮廊剪就冇再俾媽子剪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家全家人都移民咗去一個新環境，媽子為咗慳錢就重新買咗一套剪髮工具返嚟幫我地兩兄弟剪，又係剪返個標準髮型，只不過冇以前剪得咁爽手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n媽我愛妳呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9485f03409619269a2703ba64d3a61694c85d1f","tid":555784,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T21:07:06.000Z","msg":"西利<br />\n用咩工具主要?"},{"pid":"37b7c6ee4c65ad02d680271e9ed2320875f82f67","tid":555784,"uid":36478,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c9485f03409619269a2703ba64d3a61694c85d1f","tid":555784,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T21:07:06.000Z","msg":"西利<br />\n用咩工具主要?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T21:08:28.000Z","msg":"犀利"},{"pid":"322176a90a698418e5ef35d4023ada8715401259","tid":555784,"uid":153524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T21:08:33.000Z","msg":"整唔見晒間房所有野"},{"pid":"bc10b1c23c51fd1c3e7396604b96f13ee983b399","tid":555784,"uid":54871,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T21:58:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"771f97d8d4e43abe8ed0ec640023f63f41217cb0"